---
interface Props {}
---
<section class="bg-surface-container-low py-stack-xl relative" id="historia" aria-labelledby="historia-title">
  <div class="container-main">
    <div class="mb-stack-xl text-center md:text-left">
      <span class="font-ui-label text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px]">O Legado Di Napoli</span>
      <h2 id="historia-title" class="font-display-lg text-5xl mt-4 mask-reveal active">Nossa linha do tempo</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mt-24">
      <!-- Vertical Line -->
      <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-[1px] timeline-line hidden md:block" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="space-y-32">
        <!-- 1987 -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between group mask-reveal">
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] text-right pr-0 md:pr-16 order-2 md:order-1 mt-8 md:mt-0">
            <span class="font-display-lg text-6xl text-primary/10 group-hover:text-primary/20 transition-colors duration-700">1987</span>
            <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-2xl mt-4">A Fundação</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant mt-4 leading-relaxed">A primeira semente plantada pela Família Rocha Bersan, trazendo a alma da Itália para o coração do Brasil.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-primary z-10 hidden md:block outline outline-8 outline-primary/5" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] order-1 md:order-2 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-video">
            <img
              alt="Foto antiga da família fundadora da Di Napoli em 1987, ambiente rústico e acolhedor"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105"
              src="/assets/history-1987.webp"
              loading="lazy"
              width="600"
              height="450"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 1995 -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between group mask-reveal" style="transition-delay: 200ms">
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] order-1 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-video">
            <img
              alt="Artesão preparando gelato artesanal com ferramentas tradicionais de madeira"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105"
              src="/assets/history-1995.webp"
              loading="lazy"
              width="600"
              height="450"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-primary z-10 hidden md:block outline outline-8 outline-primary/5" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] text-left pl-0 md:pl-16 mt-8 md:mt-0">
            <span class="font-display-lg text-6xl text-primary/10 group-hover:text-primary/20 transition-colors duration-700">1995</span>
            <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-2xl mt-4">A União de Saberes</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant mt-4 leading-relaxed">A chegada da Família Marchi refinou nossas receitas, unindo o melhor da cafeteria tradicional com o gelato artesanal.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2010 -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between group mask-reveal" style="transition-delay: 400ms">
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] text-right pr-0 md:pr-16 order-2 md:order-1 mt-8 md:mt-0">
            <span class="font-display-lg text-6xl text-tertiary/10 group-hover:text-tertiary/20 transition-colors duration-700">2010</span>
            <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-2xl mt-4">Expansão</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant mt-4 leading-relaxed">Novas unidades e a modernização do nosso espaço, mantendo a essência artesanal.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-tertiary z-10 hidden md:block outline outline-8 outline-tertiary/5" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] order-1 md:order-2 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-video">
            <img
              alt="Inauguração de nova unidade Di Napoli com arquitetura moderna e tijolos aparentes"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105"
              src="/assets/history-2010.webp"
              loading="lazy"
              width="600"
              height="450"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2021 -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between group mask-reveal" style="transition-delay: 600ms">
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] order-1 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-video">
            <img
              alt="Redesign da marca Di Napoli com nova identidade visual mantendo tradição"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105"
              src="/assets/history-2021.webp"
              loading="lazy"
              width="600"
              height="450"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-tertiary z-10 hidden md:block outline outline-8 outline-tertiary/5" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] text-left pl-0 md:pl-16 mt-8 md:mt-0">
            <span class="font-display-lg text-6xl text-tertiary/10 group-hover:text-tertiary/20 transition-colors duration-700">2021</span>
            <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-2xl mt-4">Evolução</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant mt-4 leading-relaxed">Redesign da marca mantendo a essência artesanal, conectando gerações.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Hoje -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between group mask-reveal" style="transition-delay: 800ms">
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] text-right pr-0 md:pr-16 order-2 md:order-1 mt-8 md:mt-0">
            <span class="font-display-lg text-6xl text-primary group-hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors duration-700">Hoje</span>
            <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-2xl mt-4">Presente</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant mt-4 leading-relaxed">Referência em qualidade e memórias afetivas, servindo milhares de famílias.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-primary z-10 hidden md:block outline outline-8 outline-primary/5" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] order-1 md:order-2 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-video">
            <img
              alt="Ambiente atual da Di Napoli com clientes desfrutando de gelatos e cafés"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105"
              src="/assets/history-hoje.webp"
              loading="lazy"
              width="600"
              height="450"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>